room_title: Escape room "The Asylum 2" by Locked In Stuart in West Palm Beach
room_description: You and your team have tracked “Krazy Karter” to an unexplored portion of the abandoned asylum but he has escaped your grasp and snared you in his operating room. You only have an hour to escape his trap before he returns to eliminate his captives. Can you and your team piece together the madness of “Krazy Karter’s” secret lair?
